# Piece Type Registry
# Format: TYPE | ICON | ID
# Used by render_map.c (icon lookup) and create_piece.c (type→id/icon)
# If you add a type, update BOTH C files that read this.

TYPE | player  | @ | player
TYPE | pet     | @ | pet
TYPE | xlector | X | xlector
TYPE | npc     | & | npc
TYPE | chest   | T | chest
TYPE | zombie  | Z | zombie
